    title="My Sadaqah Online Makes Qurbani 2025 Easy & Secure"

    description="As we approach Eid ul-Adha, Muslims around the world are preparing to fulfil the important obligation of Qurbani. Qurbani, or the act of sacrificing an animal in the name of Allah (SWT), is a key part of the Eid celebration."
    image="/assets/images/home.jpg"
  />

